  "text": "The last assumption, (4f), is trivial in our construction, since at no point in the renormalization of the integrated operators have we considered the wedge state on which they are embedded. By constructing the counterterms using the local OPE rather than the two-point functions, we have avoided any difficulties that this assumption may have caused. It is here that our approach differs from that in work [CITATION_1] .",
